when there are other people in the room.

00:17.350 --> 00:19.936
And all I can do is sit and twiddle,

00:20.020 --> 00:22.689
which is what I call
my self-stimulatory behavior,

00:22.772 --> 00:27.360
when I flick a pencil against
a rubber band at a certain frequency

00:27.444 --> 00:29.529
and think about all the things that
I could never do,

00:29.612 --> 00:34.075
